README for Uncoupled NUOPC wrapped Noah LSM Test Case
---------------------------------------

Dependencies:
  - ESMF v7.0.0 beta
  
Build:
  - Set environment variable ESMFMKFILE to point to the esmf.mk of your ESMF
    installation.
  - gmake
  - outputs noahSingleModel.exe

Code structure:
  - Makefile	- Makefile that is based on the standard esmf.mk mechanism.
  - noahlsm		- Links to noahlsm-vN.N.N, The static fortran Noah LSM 
  				linked in during compiling
  - README - This file
